name: Even UFOs have accidents!
description: Have you ever wondered why it’s taking the aliens so long to reach Earth?? They get into accidents just like we do w/our cars & it’s creating traffic delays! 20 limited ed # are at a SETI price of 2.059 TEZ based on the year they will probably finally reach us. If you are a believer and want to bring in good vibes towards our planet, then this token is for you!
